                <a href="http://www.interplay.com/games/descent.php">Descent</a> video game.
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>First Image:</b> Laser cutting the Class 1 Drone.
                <br /><br />
                <b>Second Image:</b> Class 1 Drone.
